# =============================================================================
#  Common Shell Configuration (sourced by both Bash and Zsh)
#
#  This is the main config file. Bash-specific config is in ~/.bashrc,
#  Zsh-specific config is in ~/.zshrc. This file handles everything shared:
#  aliases, functions, environment setup, and tool configuration.
#
#  Layout:
#    1. Aliases         -- shortcuts for common commands
#    2. Functions       -- reusable shell functions
#    3. Environment     -- PATH, env vars, tool init
#    4. Work config     -- employer/project-specific (loaded from private repo)
# =============================================================================


# ============================================================================
#  1. Aliases
# ============================================================================

